## Description {#details}

Represents an signed integer range &#91;<a href="#ae3064cf7e3c0ba55a60729c96e524642">Range.getBegin()</a>, <a href="#ada696071634a4b785b72900b4845d1d0">Range.getEnd()</a>).

If R.getEnd() le R.getBegin(), then R denotes the empty range.
